date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"edate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"zq\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Aggregation period. Valid values: 'day', 'week', 'month', 'year'. Defaults to 'week'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"lx\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Channel type filter. 'ALL'=all channels, '1'=沪股通, '2'=港股通(沪市), '3'=深股通, '4'=港股通(深市). Defaults to 'ALL'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"bz\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Currency for amounts. Defaults to 'CNY'.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 715.71,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.532\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4\",\n      \"name\": \"Live (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve live or delayed stock prices and macroeconomic data.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"ticker\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional filter parameter.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"ticker\": \"AAPL.US\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1207.16,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.946\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.smart_stock_picking.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺智能选股 (THS Intelligent Stock Picking)\",\n      \"description\": \"同花顺 (THS) intelligent stock picking tool that supports filtering stocks in the market through natural language queries. Users can use descriptive query statements to quickly obtain stock data that meets the criteria, including stock codes, names, company cities, concepts, and detailed explanations.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"searchstring\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Natural language search query, e.g., '属于杭州的deepseek概念公司'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 988.17,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.812\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.company_basics.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 公司基础信息 (Company Basics)\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve the latest (or a specific date) company basics indicators from THS iFinD. Includes company name, industry, comparable/peer companies, concept tags, codes, established date, registration info, main business, and major products.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, comma-separated (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Date, format: 'YYYYMMDD'. Use this field to query historical values. Defaults to latest.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 780.08,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.914\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.financial_statements.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺财报 Financial Statements (Balance/Income/Cash Flow)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query balance sheet, income statement, or cash flow statement data for securities from THS iFinD Financial Statement database using a single entry point.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"statement_type\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Which statement to query: 'balance', 'income', or 'cash_flow'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"year\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Year, e.g., '2024'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"period\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Reporting period: '0331' (Q1), '0630' (H1), '0930' (Q3), '1231' (Annual)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"type\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Report type: '1' (Consolidated), '2' (Parent Company), '3' (Consolidated Adjusted), '4' (Parent Company Adjusted)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 654.98,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.877\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.report_query.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺证券公告查询 (THS Security Announcement Query)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query security announcements in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, supporting filtering and searching by security code, date range, and keywords. Users can input security codes (e.g., '920000.BJ'), announcement keywords (e.g., 'annual report'), and date ranges (e.g., '2024-10-25' to '2025-10-25') to quickly obtain detailed information about relevant announcements, including announcement date, security code, security name, release time, announcement title, announcement link, and unique identifier.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security code, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '920000.BJ'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"keyword\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Announcement keyword for searching announcement titles, default is empty string\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"beginrDate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date, format: 'YYYY-MM-DD'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"endrDate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date, format: 'YYYY-MM-DD'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"codes\": \"920000.BJ\",\n          \"endrDate\": \"2025-10-25\",\n          \"beginrDate\": \"2024-10-25\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 812.59,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.441\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.code_converter.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺证券代码转换 (THS Security Code Converter)\",\n      \"description\": \"Convert security codes or security names to 同花顺 (THS) standard code format. Supports querying by security code or security name, can specify security type and market, supports exact match or fuzzy match. Returns converted THS codes and related security information.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"seccode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Security code, e.g., '000001'. Either seccode or secname\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"secname\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Security name, e.g., '平安银行'. Either seccode or secname\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"mode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Query mode: 'seccode' (query by code) or 'secname' (query by name)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sectype\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Security type, e.g., '001' (stock), default is empty (query all types)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"market\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Market code, e.g., '212001' (SSE), '212100' (SZSE), default is empty (query all markets)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tradestatus\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Trading status: '0' (normal trading), '1' (suspended), '2' (all), default is '0'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"isexact\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Exact match: '1' (exact match), '0' (fuzzy match), default is '1'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"mode\": \"seccode\",\n          \"seccode\": \"000001\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 582.28,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.98\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub_io_api.stock.quote\",\n      \"name\": \"Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Get real-time quote data for US stocks.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Stock symbol\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 853.46,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.951\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"514a1886-57c3-4c2e-8ce2-964d3b470736\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 434.16\n}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772594548285}}
